 padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 12/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1208-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Eriksen thay Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid mua Christian Eriksen trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Luka Modric t\u1edbi Inter Milan, theo The Sun Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Daily v\u00e0 Sunday Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Inter th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Inter c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Modric mu\u1ed1n anh t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" title=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Alvaro-Morata-phat-bieu-ve-Mateo-Kovacic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Modric khuy\u00ean Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf Stamford Bridge ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Luka Modric c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi-180-194183.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi-180-194183.html\">B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Marcelo cho Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo cho Juventus. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real quan t\u00e2m Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Martial\" title=\"tien dao Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real t\u00ednh mua Thiago thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2275","checkdouble":"194328"},{"date":"09:18 12/08","title":"HLV Inter th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-luciano-spalletti-khong-tin-inter-milan-co-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chievo vs Pescara l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia QG Coppa Italia 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Pescara 23h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Coppa Italia 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Pescara 23h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Coppa Italia 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Chievo-vs-Pescara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chievo vs Pescara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Chievo vs Pescara: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nChievo t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pescara \u1edf 4/5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, Chievo c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Serie A trong khi Pescara ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ea1i Serie B. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Chievo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, tuy v\u1eady ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch trong \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Coppa Italia, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c CLB thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n trung b\u00ecnh \u1edf Italia th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Chievo c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli v\u00e0 Hoffenheim c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n thua cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a \u201cl\u1eeba bay\u201d. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong khi tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pescara l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. Pescara \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, n\u00ean tin v\u00e0o Pescara.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2274","checkdouble":"194295"},{"date":"09:23 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham (19h30 ng\u00e0y 12/8): Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb b\u1ed9i chi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-west-ham-19h30-ngay-128-tran-chien-cua-nhung-ke-boi-chi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 The Klopp t\u1ecf r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \"tranh b\u00e1\" \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eeb West Ham<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8, West Ham chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 11 t\u00e2n binh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong nh\u00f3m Big Six. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool, c\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong nh\u00f3m top 6 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng West Ham trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Manuel Pellegrini nhan dinh Liverpool vs West Ham la co hoi de doi bong cua ong the hien tham vong.\" title=\"Manuel Pellegrini nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/pellegrini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Manuel Pellegrini nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Manuel Pellegrini kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh West Ham \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ngay t\u1eeb h\u00e8 n\u00e0y: &quot;Khi th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Manuel Pellegrini c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Liverpool. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, West Ham \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1ee9 hai, HLV Pellegrini s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Liverpool ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac chuyen gia nhan dinh Liverpool vs West Ham la thach thuc nhung cung la co hoi chung minh ban than cua ca hai doi.\" title=\"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/liver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Pellegrini c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi West Ham. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, West Ham s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby Jurgen Klopp gi\u0103ng ra. Ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Liverpool lu\u00f4n \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng khi Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 Salah - Firmino - Sadio Mane, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 West Ham c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Pellegrini c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Jurgen Klopp n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1eebng b\u1eebng s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp lo lang khi Liverpool khung hoang hang thu truoc tran mo man Premier League 2018-19.\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp lo l\u1eafng khi Liverpool kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/klopp-chua-dam-dat-liverpool-ngang-hang-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp lo l\u1eafng khi Liverpool kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u01b0\u1ee1i tr\u1eafng tay c\u00f9ng Liverpool. S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o The Klopp \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Klopp, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh. Klopp c\u0169ng b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Liverpool c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m t\u1ef1 b\u1eafn v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu khi Klopp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0o khu trung tuy\u1ebfn g\u1ed3m Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho. M\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &quot;Messi trong khung g\u1ed7&quot; l\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf sai l\u1ea7m. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Shaqiri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Liverpool vs West Ham\" title=\"Preview Liverpool vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-west-ham-19h30-ngay-128-tran-chien-cua-nhung-ke-boi-chi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs West Ham - cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb b\u1ed9i chi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 hay ch\u01b0a?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Liverpool th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111\u1ec1u ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (61 l\u1ea7n, b\u1eb1ng Everton).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ed1 45 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Anh (h\u00f2a 12, thua 32). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2015.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* West Ham thua trong 11 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Sadio Mane \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong ba tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League (1 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool: </strong>Alex Oxlade Chamberlain, Ragnar Klavan ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Dejan Lovren, Joseph Gomez, Joel Matip, Fabinho, James Milner ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>West Ham:</strong> Winston Reid, Manuel Lanzini, Andy Carroll ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Carlos Sanchez, Lucas Perez, Andriy Yarmolenko ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Liverpool vs West Ham (19h30 ng\u00e0y 12/8):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool (4-3-3):</strong> 13.Alisson - 66.Alexander-Arnold, 12. Joe Gomez, 4.Van Dijk, 26.A.Robertson - 5.Wijnaldum, 14.Henderson, 8.Naby Keita - 10.Mane, 9.Firmino, 11.Salah</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>West Ham (4-3-3): </strong>1.Fabianski - 5.Zabaleta, 23.Diop, 21.Ogbonna, 3.Cresswell - 14.Obiang, 16.Noble, 19.Wilshere - 20.Yarmolenko, 8.Anderson, 7.Arnautovic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Liverpool 4-2 West Ham<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu-172-194284.html\">Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Liverpool xo\u00e1y s\u00e2u v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-tu-choi-ban-hang-thai-cho-newcastle-172-194271.html\">HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i cho Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-quyet-chung-to-gia-tri-cua-mot-bom-tan-172-194269.html\">Alisson quy\u1ebft ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc-172-194241.html\">Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-liverpool-he-2018-172-194217.html\">S\u1eafm s\u1eeda xong xu\u00f4i, gi\u1edd Klopp mu\u1ed1n d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2273","checkdouble":"194296"},{"date":"09:45 12/08","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ra v\u00ed nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Man United hay kh\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2, n\u01a1i anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2018/19. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester City, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n 4 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nL\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 tin Barcelona v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Juventus r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tin \u0111\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m vui t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Anh v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb HLV Jose Mourinho, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Champions League v\u1edbi Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 8, Pogba v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U. Chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho c\u00e1c CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng Barca hay Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U hay kh\u00f4ng, Paul Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t. Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Pogba c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Instagram: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra\u201d, anh vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho-172-194161.html\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho-172-194161.html\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2272","checkdouble":"194297"},{"date":"09:27 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Pescara 23h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Coppa Italia 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-chievo-vs-pescara-23h00-ngay-128-coppa-italia-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chievo vs Pescara l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia QG Coppa Italia 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Pescara 23h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Coppa Italia 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Pescara 23h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Coppa Italia 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Chievo-vs-Pescara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chievo vs Pescara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Chievo vs Pescara: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nChievo t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pescara \u1edf 4/5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, Chievo c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Serie A trong khi Pescara ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ea1i Serie B. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Chievo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, tuy v\u1eady ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch trong \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Coppa Italia, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c CLB thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n trung b\u00ecnh \u1edf Italia th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Chievo c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli v\u00e0 Hoffenheim c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n thua cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a \u201cl\u1eeba bay\u201d. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong khi tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pescara l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. Pescara \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, n\u00ean tin v\u00e0o Pescara.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2271","checkdouble":"194298"},{"date":"09:56 12/08","title":"Sarri ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1eeba ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Huddersfield.</h2><h2>Chelsea th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Huddersfield\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a N&rsquo;golo Kante, Jorginho v\u00e0 Pedro \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Huddersfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Arsenal. V\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Sarri-ball nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng nhanh h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p hai khi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn v\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c 1 tr\u1eadn m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y. Khi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m. Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi b\u1ecb ng\u1ee3p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m m\u1ec7t v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p hai&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea:\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2270","checkdouble":"194299"}]}